Textarea field with "django-filebrowser-no-grappelli" support.

Usage:
-----
 *  Install "django-sakkada"
 *  Install "django-filebrowser-no-grappelli"
    (https://pypi.python.org/pypi/django-filebrowser-no-grappelli)
 *  Import "sakkada.admin.editors.simple_fb.EditorAdmin"
 *  Set "EditorAdmin" as class of admin model
 *  Define "simple_fb_fields" param for required fields
 *  Copy static "admin/simple_fb/*" and "filebrowser/js/FB_FileBrowseField.js"
    (to override default "FB_FileBrowseField.js") to your project static folder
    or add "sakkada.admin.editors.simple_fb" to your INSTALLED_APPS before
    "filebrowser".

Example usage:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
from django.contrib import admin
from sakkada.admin.editors.simple_fb import EditorAdmin


class SomeAdmin(EditorAdmin, admin.ModelAdmin):
    simple_fb_fields = ('text',)

admin.site.register(Some, SomeAdmin)
